  "title": "Production Operator (Manufacturing)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Location:</strong> Tuas, Singapore<br /><strong>Free Company Shuttle</strong> from Choa Chu Kang & Joo Koon MRT stations.</p><ul><li><p><strong>4-Day Work Week</strong> | <strong>5-Day Work Week</strong> | <strong>6-Day Work Week</strong></p></li></ul><ul><li><p><strong>Day :</strong> 7:30 AM – 7:30 PM</p></li><li><p><strong>Night :</strong> 7:30 PM – 7:30 AM<br />*All shifts include a 1-hour meal break + two paid 15-minute rest breaks.*</p></li></ul><ul><li><p>Run and monitor automated production equipment safely and efficiently.</p></li><li><p>Perform regular quality checks to ensure top-tier standards.</p></li><li><p>Record simple, accurate production data.</p></li><li><p>Maintain a clean, organized, and safe workspace.</p></li><li><p>Follow clear procedures to deliver consistent, reliable output.</p></li></ul><ul><li><p><strong>Base Salary:</strong> $2,500 – $3,300/month (based on experience)</p></li><li><p><strong>Extra Earnings:</strong> Night shift allowance (up to $25/night) + overtime pay</p></li><li><p><strong>Annual Rewards:</strong> 13th-month salary + performance bonus (typically 1–2 months)</p></li></ul><p></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p><br /></p><p>EA Personnel R22110043 Tan Eng Kang</p><p>EA License 21C0430 A Dreamworks Company Pte Ltd</p>",
